The article is a letter from President Joseph R. Biden Jr. to the Chairman (or Chairwoman) of a committee. It states that the letter is in accordance with a specific section of the National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2018. The purpose of the letter is to inform about changes to the legal and policy frameworks for the United States' use of military force and national security operations related to recent military operations against Iran-aligned militia groups. The letter also mentions the enclosure of a classified annex. The letter is signed by President Joseph R. Biden Jr.